{"tid":807300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 西鐵線列車故障　港人只擔心 \"遲到被老闆炒！\"","createTime":"2018-09-05T11:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T01:46:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0a4f6d6932a64a2ce35ad3af3a8f3ebbed9b9f7d","tid":807300,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:44:03.000Z","msg":"黎先生約9時半於朗屏站上車，原定10時半前到達柯士甸站上班。惟因列車故障，估計行程延誤約半小時。他指，事故令其上班遲到半小時，須先向公司報備，「老闆<span style=\"color: red;\">都有話我，就嚟畀人炒啦！</span>」他批評，港鐵安排差，未有及早向乘客通報，令其上車後才得悉列車故障，「早啲知會轉其他交通工具。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/194347_73059fd2be18dce030a2291730754aab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F194347_73059fd2be18dce030a2291730754aab.png&h=6cca7241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/231620/西鐵線列車故障-乘客批評港鐵安排差-遲到被老闆炒\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F231620%2F%E8%A5%BF%E9%90%B5%E7%B7%9A%E5%88%97%E8%BB%8A%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%B7%AE-%E9%81%B2%E5%88%B0%E8%A2%AB%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E7%82%92&d=MWJ%2FoQsH6fUX2op4UrBM2kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ccef1962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/231620/西鐵線列車故障-乘客批評港鐵安排差-遲到被老闆炒</a>"},{"pid":"c65cfde04d95064ee6f22cfa2adda87be4035857","tid":807300,"uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"slave<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfa874593a316b08559c42e2541bd2b071e6fe2","tid":807300,"uid":5178,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"睇字都覺得佢壓力好大"},{"pid":"0aff1b04f9dcdf4697078128bb0d0